Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.84,0:00:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You absolutely sure\Nyou can do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.37,0:00:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! Wouldn't have\Nagreed to it if I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.75,0:00:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.04,0:00:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of cake, I got a little\Nsomething I need to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.14,0:00:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like keeping an eye\Non a house full of critters.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah, that was totally\Nwhat I was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.01,0:00:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax! Go to your welcoming\Nthing in the Crystal Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike's got it all under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, Twilight!\NWe can't miss our train!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.11,0:00:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.55,0:00:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is gonna be a real treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.61,0:00:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Cadance said she'd never seen\Nthe Crystal Ponies so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.59,0:00:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course they're excited.\NThey're up for the Equestria Games!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.61,0:00:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only the biggest sporting\Nevent in all of Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't Cloudsdale host\Nthe Equestria Games one year?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.04,0:00:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Cloudsdale should have\Nhosted the games one year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.95,0:01:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget\Nwhen we got the bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Equestria Games go to...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the city of Fillydelphia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.41,0:01:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,NOOOOOOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.95,0:01:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,These Crystal Ponies lost a thousand\Nyears to an evil King's curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.66,0:01:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They've had enough bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.19,0:01:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No way we're letting them experience\Nthe pain of losing out on these games.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.91,0:01:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.09,0:01:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Cadance is counting on us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.01,0:01:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to do our part to convince\Nthe Games Inspector
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.09,0:01:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,to choose the Crystal Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.64,0:01:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And we are not gonna\Nlet her down. Are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.15,0:01:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,NOOOOOOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.61,0:01:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I was just answering\NTwilight's question.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.68,0:01:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Season 3 | Episode 12\NGames Ponies Play
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.57,0:01:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Subbed by GrayJeager\NFr.Jeager@gmail.com
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,http://www.youtube.com/user/GrayJeager3\Nhttp://www.youtube.com/user/GhxBronie\Nhttp://grayjeager.blogspot.fr (french)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.88,0:02:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Four, three, two, one,\Nthe Crystal Empire, that's the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, everypony, great job!\NSounds like we're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time, from the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.28,0:02:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please.\NI think that was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.60,0:02:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we've run this like\Ntwelve times already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.52,0:02:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Cadance said the Games Inspector
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,really puts folks through\Nthe wringer on her visits.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.67,0:02:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no margin for error here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.62,0:02:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And this time we need\Nto practice the steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.92,0:02:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,On a train car?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.09,0:02:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard the pony!\NOn your hooves!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Two, four, six, eight--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Crystal Empire, ladies!\NWatch your step leaving the train!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably should've watched our step\Nwhile we were still on it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The Crystal Empire\Nlooks crystallier than ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They must have every pony\Nin the Empire out sprucing it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.86,0:03:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be why we are asked to handle\Nthe welcome committee routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.25,0:03:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's probably also because\Nwe'll be awesome at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Cadance was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,These ponies\Ndo look pretty darn excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, I remember that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But not as much as I remember
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.57,0:03:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the crushing wave of disappointment\Nthat came when things didn't work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.95,0:03:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the face\NI do not want to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There are my girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunshine, sunshine,\Nladybugs awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Clap your hooves\Nand do a little shake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my.\NThis is spectacular.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, everypony, stand back!\NI need air!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.87,0:04:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and try whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.92,0:04:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all complimentary\Nfor the welcome committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That over there\Nis a crystal mud bath,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,which relaxes your body\Nand rejuvenates your coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I realize it can be kind\Nof strange to climb into mud,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you'll just give it a chance,\NI'm sure--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so relaxing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie, honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, have a good time while\NI get my ceremonial headdress done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ceremonial... headdress?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,When meeting\Nwith important guests,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,it was tradition for\Nrulers of the Crystal Empire
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to weave crystals into their manes\Nin a very specific way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The Games Inspector is known\Nfor doing her homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll certainly be expecting my look\Nto reflect the importance of her visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.72,0:05:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If I may have a word,\NI have two pieces of news for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,First, your mane stylist has the flu\Nand won't be able to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.67,0:05:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,for fear of you catching it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope she's better soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.86,0:05:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do any of the other\Nstylists here know
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.97,0:05:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,how to do the traditional\Nroyal ceremonial headdress?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.12,0:05:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a small detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.08,0:05:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to land\Nthe Equestria Games here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no such thing\Nas a small detail!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.23,0:05:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.57,0:05:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose...\NI could give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.32,0:05:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Rarity,\Nyou would do that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to step it up, Rare!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, I have all\Nthe precise instructions right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure you're up to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Working on the hair of royalty\Non such an auspicious occasion
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,is the opportunity of a lifetime!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I will give it\Neverything I've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,See? No worries!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.07,0:06:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, the Games Inspector\Nisn't expected for several hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.76,0:06:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have plenty of time to figure out\Nexactly how to... do... this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Rarity, that's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.15,0:06:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You said\Nyou had a second bit of news?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, quite.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The Games Inspector, Ms. Harshwhinny,\Nwill be arriving on the... next train.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.62,0:06:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What!? You couldn't have\Ntold us that news first!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.69,0:06:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fifteen minutes from now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How long before Cadance is ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure to find some shortcuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you have her back at the castle\Nwhen we're done?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:06:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:07:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony, just look out for the pony\Nwith the flower print luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.22,0:07:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy peasy, pudding in the freezy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll bring the Games Inspector\Nback to the castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,put on our big welcome committee\Nhow-do-you-do and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.71,0:07:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Put the pudding out to thaw before\Nyou eat it or you'll crack a tooth?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just ignore that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.67,0:07:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to remember that\Nthe Games Inspector arriving early
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is probably part of a plan\Nto psyche us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.97,0:07:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it yourself, she's got a rep\Nfor catching hosts off-guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to see if we can handle\Nthe kind of massive pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.67,0:07:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that comes with hosting\Nthe Equestria Games!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...\NWe're gonna blow it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Not if we always stay one step ahead\Nand don't fall for any of her mind games.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.26,0:07:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything she throws at us,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,we just needs to remember\Nshe's testing us and roll with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, no!\N- Be cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I know you're not expecting us,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.30,0:08:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but we're here to personally\Nwelcome you to the Crystal Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.85,0:08:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole lot of you\Ncame to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well, um, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, darn tootin',\Nain't that the cat's meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.16,0:08:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'all didn't need to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, I hardly expected\Nanything like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Princess wouldn't have had it\Nany other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The Princess? Princess Cadance?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,None other!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, tie me up and throw me down,\Nthis just keeps gettin' better and better!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can we help you with your bags?\N- Don't mind if you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, I love flower print!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.02,0:08:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Our first stop is the castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.81,0:08:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,where we got a razzamatazzy\Nwelcome planned for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.71,0:08:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The castle? Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot-diggety-dawg!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:09:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,See that?\NWe just gotta roll with it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.61,0:09:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,until the Princess gets there\Nand we'll be just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.33,0:09:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So, uh... how's it going so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.23,0:09:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm so sorry...\NIt's just... so complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- I can fix it!\N- Fix what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.91,0:09:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I was looking for shortcuts\Nand I thought step twelve was optional!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,My golly, the crystal castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen pictures but I never expected\Nto see it with my very own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.01,0:09:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,From the inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.98,0:09:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh, she's so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:10:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're letting her lull you\Ninto a false sense of confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch that.\NIt's all part of the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, I'm so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, have a seat, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind if I take\Na quick run outside first?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an awfully long train ride\Nand my legs could use a stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.19,0:10:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well...\NWe were just about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Never you mind.\NYou go on ahead. I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She was probably testing us to see
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,if we could remain in control\Nof a complex situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.25,0:10:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd like to thank you\Nfor this opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to introduce you\Nto this wonderful kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, the pleasure is all mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And since we're not even\Nfrom here ourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,who better than us to let you know\Njust how welcoming this place can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.82,0:10:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Two, four, six, eight!\NName a place that's really great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four!\NKeeps you coming back for more!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Two, seven, nine, three!\NThe place that we all wanna be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Four, three, two, one!\NThe Crystal Empire, that's the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.55,0:11:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I tell ya!\NI have travelled far and wide,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have never ever\Nbeen welcomed anyplace
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,in the fashion y'all have\Ndone here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.55,0:11:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.27,0:11:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Cadance\Nwill be so glad to hear that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I'm surprised\Nshe knows anything about me at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.76,0:11:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course she does!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been looking forward\Nto your visit for weeks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, goody! Is she here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.37,0:11:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the heck is she, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.18,0:11:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't she supposed\Nto be here by now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.54,0:11:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe-- I'll just take\Nmy little run outside now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, if you like, we could\Ngive you a tour of the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That way you could be learning\Nand stretching all at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.34,0:12:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A tour of the crystal castle...\NI'd love that a whole heap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dash! We've hardly\Never even been here before!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just another test!\NWe gotta roll with it, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.30,0:12:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemme give the tour!\NI'lldoit, I'lldoit, letmeletmeletme!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You all start giving her the tour\Nand I'll go see what's keeping Cadance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hello there!\N- Hello yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,First hello of the day--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We finished\Nthe welcome committee song
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and we just wanted to introduce\NMs. Harshwhinny to--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Cadance isn't ready.\NSomething's gone terribly wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- I need to speak to the Princess.\N- You can't! You musn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in the middle of\Na delicate conditioning rinse
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.93,0:12:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that must go perfectly\Nif there's to be any hope for her hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, how bad can it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine her mane\Nturned into a porcupine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I will bring her back\Nfrom the brink of tragedy,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but you have got\Nto buy me some time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.86,0:13:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you see this here?\NThis, um, this is, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,a big, round room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's known for its roundness.\NAnd bigness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And did I mention that it's... round?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they call it a rotunda?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.08,0:13:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A small, confining, rotunda...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.\NRound is round, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy, Pinkie,\Nlet's play this safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We got her in a good mood,\Nso let's not do anything to ruin that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You know...\NI love this sort of architecture,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I detect a neo-gothic\Ninspiration in the design, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.21,0:13:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And not a moment too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.58,0:13:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Cadance?\NPlease tell me she's right behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:13:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a bit of a problem\Nwith her headdress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it going here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.83,0:14:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I, uh, hate to be a bother,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but the legs are cramping up on me\Nwith all this standing around...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She's getting bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And we have\Nto buy Rarity some more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see\Nif Shining Armor can come help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't one of you other ponies\Ntake over in the meantime?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna stretch your legs, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever you need,\NI'm sure we can provide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.39,0:14:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just make our way\Nto the castle's gymnasium.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.04,0:14:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Our tour will now be headed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're walking,\Nand we're walking...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.96,0:14:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Twily!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.31,0:14:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.90,0:14:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Shining Armor,\Nyou've gotta help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:14:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.06,0:15:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I left the other ponies behind\Ngiving the Games Inspector
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.51,0:15:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the worst castle tour ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, gang!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we gonna gallop,\Nor are we gonna trot!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.64,0:15:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Castle tour, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure\NI can give you a hoof with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.04,0:15:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's move, move, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.90,0:15:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I'm not worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.26,0:15:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not worried... it worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.27,0:15:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Feels so good\Nto stretch the old legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, what the--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.30,0:15:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Turns out the crystal castle\Ndoesn't have a gymnasium.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.86,0:15:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.94,0:15:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Make her stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, that's the Games Inspector!\NLet her do her thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, these hooves! I'm outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- Why would she do that?\N- I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.08,0:15:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But, that's why she's in charge\Nof choosing who gets the Games,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.16,0:15:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.67,0:15:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, get me outside for a run!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.89,0:16:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay, we need to stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.23,0:16:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's she going in such a hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Closer... closer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.97,0:16:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we've got her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.19,0:16:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that felt good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing like a great run to shake\Nthe cobwebs off these old bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there, speedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.69,0:16:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, these wide open spaces\Ny'all got here remind me of home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.88,0:16:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! So you're...\Nenjoying your visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.87,0:16:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm so... glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:17:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh good golly, yes, I just love\Nto travel and see new places.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.26,0:17:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a beautiful spot\Nyou got here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... thank you so much!\NI'm Shining Armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.91,0:17:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's going on?\N- From the looks of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,just locking up the games\Nfor the Crystal Empire is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't no thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My oh my...\NI never met a Prince before...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd think in your line of work,\Nyou'd meet princes all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Just an ordinary\Nwild mustang from Mustangia
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,here to enjoy a little vay-cay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.38,0:17:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Never thought I'd also\Nbe meeting royalty to boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Ms. Harshwhinny,\Nthe Equestria Games Inspector,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.32,0:17:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector what-now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.14,0:17:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We got the wrong pony?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:17:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,NOOOOOOOOOOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.99,0:17:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean,\NYEEEEEEESSSSSSSS!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please still be here...\Noh please oh please oh please...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There's got to be another pony
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,with flower print luggage\Naround here somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Except that there isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gotta find her\Nbefore Cadance finds out
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.04,0:18:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,what a mess\Nwe've made of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.76,0:18:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, here's what we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We split the Empire up\Ninto five sectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Each of us search a sector.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.69,0:18:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Except for the spa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point of checking there?\NThat's where Cadance is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If Ms. Harshwhinny is there,\Nwell, then, game over, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.20,0:18:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Every city and empire\Nwants to host the Equestria Games!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.44,0:18:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I have to go through all the\Nbig phony-baloney song and dance,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.71,0:18:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,though of course, I'm never\Ngetting the real inside scoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, golly I've been having\Na swell time since I got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually thinking of extendin'\Nmy stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.23,0:18:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And what exactly\Nhas made your visit so special?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:18:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh, where to start?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think either of them knows yet\Nthat the other one's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful news, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Cadance,\Nbetter than new!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.12,0:19:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Cadance?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is where you've been!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.27,0:19:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I will have you know
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.90,0:19:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,this is by far the worst welcome\NI've had in all my years!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.23,0:19:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I can't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What was wrong\Nwith your welcome?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.82,0:19:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.16,0:19:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess, we gave our welcome\Nto the wrong pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Left the right one\Nwaiting at the station,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and completely ruined everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.12,0:19:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Cinnamon bun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:19:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was a little filly,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted so badly for Cloudsdale\Nto win the Equestria Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it didn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.66,0:19:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought I could make up\Nfor that disappointment
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,by helping the Crystal Empire win\Nthe chance to host the Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:20:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But it looks like\NI ruined your chances instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast, speedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I just finished hearing about how this pony\Nwas just treated to the warmest,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.81,0:20:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,finest, most fabulous reception\Nshe ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn tootin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Courtesy of these fine ponies\Nright here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Which, in my expert opinion,\Namounts to the first ever
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,unvarnished, unrehearsed,\Nand unbiased appraisal
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.41,0:20:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,of a potential host\Nof the Equestria Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.96,0:20:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Which can only mean one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The next host\Nof the Equestria Games is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Crystal Empire!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.28,0:20:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.80,0:20:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Congratulations, crystal ponies!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,\Nit feels good to help others
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.56,0:20:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,get something you always wanted\Nbut never had.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost as good as getting it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.36,0:20:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll still be able to come back here\Nand watch the games when they're played.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.56,0:21:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. That'll rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.56,0:21:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All aboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.71,0:21:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Bummer Spike\Nhad to miss out on all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.70,0:21:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He woulda' had fun here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.31,0:21:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he's having a great time\Nwatching all the critters back at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.07,0:21:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Think he's still got\Na handle on things?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.22,0:21:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's staying calm\Nand collected,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.51,0:21:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet he's doing\Na terrific job as a leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.75,0:21:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You all hear that?
